freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Arm numbness and tingling (side of injection)

Numbness and tingling in left hand (side of injection).   Started very slightly after first injection, more pronounced over last 2 weeks since second injection. Unrelated to limb position, activity, time, etc. Never had thia before.
Worsening arm numbness.  Worsening hand tingling. And itchiness of distal digits 2,3 &4
